THIS REMARKABLE PROPERTY is located in the highly sought after enclave of The Sanctuary in P.B. Gardens. PrimaryBR/BA + Den & CabanaBA on 1st Flr. 3BR/2BA on 2nd Flr. NEW ROOF(2023), 3CAR GARAGE, 3ZONE A/C. Complete Storm Protection (Elec.& Folding), a Spacious Lanai, Pool & Spa. Situated for privacy &  bordering on a Nature Preserve, this home radiates a serene atmosphere. Rarely available YORK model by PULTE Homes provides the perfect blend of luxury & natural beauty & boasts high ceilings, charming loft upstairs & elegant oak floors throughout the main level. The large open kitchen adds modern sophistication to this already impressive property, creating a perfect blend of style & functionality. Conveniently located near Shopping, Dining, Beaches, I95 & PBI Airport.MAKE THIS HOME YOURS! Features List:
NEW ROOF/2023

3 A/C Units
(April, 2007:Downstairs Hall. May2010:Laundry Rm. Sept.,2012 Upstairs.)
